---
import Button from '../Button.astro'
---

<section
  id="hero-section"
  class="rounded-header relative overflow-hidden bg-gradient-to-r from-dark via-dark-900 to-dark pb-12 md:pb-20 lg:pb-32"
>
  <!-- 背景装饰 -->
  <div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-10">
    <div
      class="absolute right-10 top-10 h-64 w-64 rounded-full bg-primary blur-3xl md:right-20 md:top-20 md:h-96 md:w-96"
    >
    </div>
    <div
      class="absolute bottom-10 left-10 h-64 w-64 rounded-full bg-blue-400 blur-3xl md:bottom-20 md:left-20 md:h-96 md:w-96"
    >
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- 英雄区域 -->
  <div
    class="relative mx-auto mt-8 max-w-5xl px-4 text-center md:mt-12 md:px-6 lg:mt-16"
  >
    <h1 class="page-title">技术展望</h1>
    <p class="text-description mx-auto mb-6 max-w-3xl px-2 md:mb-8 lg:mb-10">
      我们依托全球技术网络，运用最新技术架构，为全球用户提供稳定、高效、安全的交易平台。探索我们的技术优势，感受科技与金融的完美融合。
    </p>
    <Button variant="primary" size="md">了解更多</Button>
  </div>
</section>
